{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<main>","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/main","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumo","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O elemento&nbsp;<strong><code>&lt;main&gt;</code></strong><code> define o conteúdo principal dentro do </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a> em seu documento ou aplicação. Entende-se como conteúdo principal aquele relacionado diretamente com o tópico central da página ou com a funcionalidade central da aplicação. O mesmo deverá ser único na página, ou seja, dentro do elemento &lt;main&gt; não deverão ser incluidas seções da página que sejam comuns a todo o site ou aplicação, tais como mecanismos de navegação, informações de copyright, logotipo e campos de busca<code> </code><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span class=\"hps\">(a não ser</span><span>, é claro,</span>&nbsp; caso <span class=\"hps\">a função principal do</span> <span class=\"hps\">documento</span> <span class=\"hps\">seja</span><span class=\"hps\">&nbsp; fazer algum tipo de busca</span><span class=\"hps\">).</span></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Nota:</strong> <code>&lt;main&gt;</code> <strong>não pode </strong>ser filho dos elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>.</p>\n\n<p><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span class=\"hps\">Autores</span> <strong><span class=\"hps\">não devem</span></strong> <span class=\"hps\">incluir mais de um</span> <span class=\"hps\">elemento main no mesmo </span><span class=\"hps\">documento<strong>.</strong></span></span></p>\n</div>\n\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a class=\"new\" href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Categorias de conteúdo</a></dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories#Flow_content\">Conteúdo de fluxo</a>, conteúdo palpável.</li>\n <li><dfn>Conteúdo permitido</dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories#Flow_content\">Conteúdo de fluxo</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Omissão de tag</dfn> Nenhuma; <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span class=\"hps\">ambas</span> <span class=\"hps\">as tags de início</span> <span class=\"hps\">e fim</span> <span class=\"hps\">são obrigatórios</span></span>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Elementos pais permitidos</dfn> Qualquer elemento que aceite <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories#Flow_content\">conteúdo de fluxo</a>, mas não pode ser filho dos elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>DOM interface</dfn> <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Este elemento admite apenas os </span><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Atributos Globais\">atributos globais</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- outro conteúdo --&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Maçãs<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>A maçã é a fruta pomácea da macieira.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Vermelho delicioso<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Estas maçãs vermelhas brilhantes são as mais comumente encontradas em muitos supermercados.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>... <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>... <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Granny Smith<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Essas suculentas maçãs verdes, são um ótimo recheio para torta de maçã.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>... <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>... <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- outro conteúdo --&gt;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estado</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#the-main-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;main&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span class=\"hps\">Removida</span> <span class=\"hps\">a restrição</span> <span class=\"hps\">sobre não usar</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">&lt;</span><span>main</span><span>&gt;</span> <span class=\"hps\">como um filho</span> <span class=\"hps\">dos elementos</span></span> <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/grouping-content.html#the-main-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;main&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>Não há mudança na <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML5' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/grouping-content.html#the-main-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;main&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Navegadores compatíveis","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span class=\"hps atn\">O </span><span>elemento</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">&lt;</span><span>main</span><span>&gt; </span></span><span lang=\"pt\"><span class=\"hps\">é amplamente suportado</span> <span class=\"hps\">(exceto pelo</span> <span class=\"hps\">Internet</span> <span class=\"hps\">Explorer).</span> <span class=\"hps\">Sugere-se</span> <span class=\"hps\">que, até</span> que o elemento <span class=\"hps atn\">&lt;main</span><span>&gt; seja</span><span class=\"hps\"> suportado pelo</span> <span class=\"hps\">Internet</span> <span class=\"hps\">Explorer, adicione a ele o atributo role com o valor \"main\"</span></span>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>main</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>main<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  ...\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>Chrome 26</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/21\" title=\"Released on 2013-05-14.\">21.0</a> (21.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>Opera 16</td>\n   <td>Safari 7</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>21.0 (21.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span class=\"hps\">Elementos estruturais básicos</span></span>: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/html\"><code>&lt;html&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/head\"><code>&lt;head&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li>Elementos relacionados a seções: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, or <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"resumo"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Navegadores compatíveis","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O elemento <main> define o conteúdo principal dentro do <body> em seu documento ou aplicação. Entende-se como conteúdo principal aquele relacionado diretamente com o tópico central da página ou com a funcionalidade central da aplicação. O mesmo deverá ser único na página, ou seja, dentro do elemento <main> não deverão ser incluidas seções da página que sejam comuns a todo o site ou aplicação, tais como mecanismos de navegação, informações de copyright, logotipo e campos de busca (a não ser, é claro,  caso a função principal do documento seja  fazer algum tipo de busca).","popularity":0.0012,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<main>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<main>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<main>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<main>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<main>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<main>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<main>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<main>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/main","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/main/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/main","title":"<main>"}],"pageTitle":"<main> - HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}